            h2 About
            
            .about
                .about-text
                    p <strong>We bring together data stewards and researchers</strong> to efficiently compose data management plans (DMPs) for their research projects.
                    p Data Stewards capture and combine their <strong>knowledge and expertise with respect</strong> to the specific needs of a domain or an organisation. Researchers are <strong>truly guided</strong> through composing a DMP which can be then exported using selected template and format, <strong>including machine-actionable</strong>.
                    p The benefit lies not only in having a nowadays often <strong>obligatory DMP for funders</strong> but mainly learning how to handle data correctly, make them <strong>FAIR</strong>, maintain them well during the project, and curate them <strong>long-term</strong>.
